parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Sender and AC AMP Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel sender and AC AMP can cause the fuel gauge to malfunction, leading to unexpected fuel depletion, engine stalling, and increased risk of accidents or injuries, especially when driving on highways.
symptoms: The fuel gauge no longer works
the vehicle stops running due to fuel depletion
the driver is unaware of the fuel level

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the steering assembly can lead to a loss of steering control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Cracking or breaking of the steering assembly without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Faulty Wiring and Electrical System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring and electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
The sudden loss of electrical power can cause the vehicle to stall or shut down, leading to a loss of control, increased risk of accidents, and potential stranding on the road.
symptoms: causing the engine to stall or shut down
and potential failure of safety features.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The erratic shifting of gears can cause the vehicle to jerk or hesitate, leading to a loss of control, increased risk of accidents, and potential damage to the transmission.
symptoms: The vehicle shifts erratically between gears
or gets stuck in a particular gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The deteriorating dashboard can cause visibility issues due to excessive glare, posing a risk to the driver's safety, especially during sunny days. The cracking and falling off of dashboard pieces can also cause a distraction or even physical harm to the driver.
symptoms: The dashboard becomes extremely shiny and sticky
glare from the dashboard makes it difficult to see out of the windshield
pieces of the dashboard crack and fall off
and are propelled by the air conditioning into the face of the driver.
